      <title>阿德尔森支持的德克萨斯州众议院议长击败初选挑战者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/adelson-backed-texas-house-speaker-holds-off-primary-challenger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州众议院议长戴德·菲兰 (Dade Phelan) 在保守派巨额捐赠者米丽亚姆·阿德尔森 (Miriam Adelson) 的帮助下击败了初选，阿德尔森的家族博彩帝国一直在推动该州赌场合法化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/adelson-backed-texas-house-speaker-holds-off-primary-challenger</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:23:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>审计发现海军 220 亿美元护卫舰设计监督“拙劣”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/navy-botched-design-oversight-of-22-billion-frigate-gao-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国国会最新审计结果显示，美国海军对价值 220 亿美元的护卫舰项目监管不力，该项目旨在取代备受批评且更脆弱的濒海战斗舰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/navy-botched-design-oversight-of-22-billion-frigate-gao-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:59:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西在紧张局势中迁走驻以色列大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/brazil-relocates-ambassador-from-israel-after-months-of-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西在加沙地带的军事行动导致两国外交关系持续数月紧张，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将巴西驻以色列大使调任至其他职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/brazil-relocates-ambassador-from-israel-after-months-of-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:28:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷面临供暖危机，1980 年以来最严重冬季即将来临</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/argentina-faces-natural-gas-crunch-with-colder-winter-setting-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着南半球冬季来临，气温低于预期，家庭供暖需求增加，阿根廷正在努力确保燃料供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/argentina-faces-natural-gas-crunch-with-colder-winter-setting-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利总统奥尔班为何阻挠盟友向乌克兰提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/why-hungary-s-orban-is-stonewalling-eu-nato-allies-over-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理在欧盟和北约军事联盟中常常显得格格不入。自俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来，维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 基本上是孤身一人，拒绝西方向基辅提供援助。战争已进入第三个年头，乌克兰急需援助，这位民族主义领袖的阻挠激怒了匈牙利的盟友，并引发了人们对其政府真正效忠对象的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/why-hungary-s-orban-is-stonewalling-eu-nato-allies-over-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:07:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在国内遭遇挫折后，米莱向硅谷推销阿根廷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/milei-pitches-argentina-to-silicon-valley-after-setbacks-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱本周将在加利福尼亚州向苹果公司、 Alphabet 公司和 Meta Platforms 公司推介在阿根廷的投资，以此借此获得前所未有的国际认可，巩固其在国内的政治实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/milei-pitches-argentina-to-silicon-valley-after-setbacks-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 13:56:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派强烈谴责马杜罗禁止欧盟监察员的举动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/venezuela-opposition-blast-maduro-s-move-to-bar-eu-monitors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派领导人表示，总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗“武断”决定不邀请欧盟选举监督员，引发了人们对七月总统选举合法性的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/venezuela-opposition-blast-maduro-s-move-to-bar-eu-monitors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 13:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列预计还需要七个月的战斗才能击败哈马斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/israel-sees-seven-more-months-of-fighting-in-gaza-until-hamas-is-crushed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国家安全顾问表示，以色列很可能无法在年底前击败哈马斯，这凸显了以色列在实现消灭加沙伊斯兰组织的既定目标方面所面临的困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/israel-sees-seven-more-months-of-fighting-in-gaza-until-hamas-is-crushed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 13:12:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
